<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Error - Something Went Wrong</title>

    <style>
      /* Body styling */
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      /* Container for the error message */
      .error-container {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        margin-top: 100px;
      }

      /* Title styling */
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5em;
        color: #d9534f;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      /* Message text styling */
      p {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      /* Link styling */
      a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 30px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }

      a:hover {
        background-color: #0056b3;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      /* Style for error stack trace and other details in development mode */
      pre {
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 1em;
        color: #333;
        overflow-x: auto;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        word-wrap: break-word;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      /* Status message styles */
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        color: #555;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      strong {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="error-container">
      <h1>Oops! Something Went Wrong</h1>
      <p>
        We're sorry, but something unexpected happened. Please try again later.
      </p>

      <h2>Error Details:</h2>
      <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= statusCode %></p>
      <p><strong>Message:</strong> <%= message %></p>

      <a href="/listings">Go Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
